sub_title: Founder Dutch AI Ethics Community || Algorithm Audit || Winner Women in AI Diversity Leader Award || 100 Brilliant Women in AI Ethics™️ - 2023
summary:
⭐️If we haven’t met yet and you would like to connect, I would appreciate it if you’d attach a small note to your invite on why we should connect :). 

⭐️I have a BSc in AI with a background in AI ethics. My mission is to mitigate (unintended) problematic decisions as much as possible and contribute to a future wherein AI empowers society, rather than exacerbate existing hidden biases and discriminatory decisions. I am also an advocate for using AI for Good and technology to help marginalized groups. My biggest professional interests lie in data, privacy, education, fairness and inclusion.
